"2017-06-28T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得漢字先係最適合廣東話 拼音個啲都係旁門左道<br />\n你個表啲新字母好似泰文咁 複雜又唔夠漢字清晰</blockquote><br />\n漢字真係又靚又好用"},{"pid":"dc071f57cb2962400b4f649566d583ddf36bcb10","tid":300869,"uid":12404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得漢字先係最適合廣東話 拼音個啲都係旁門左道<br />\n你個表啲新字母好似泰文咁 複雜又唔夠漢字清晰</blockquote><br />\n漢字真係又靚又好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有兩個方向可以做<br />\n<br />\n1. 假名化，好似樓主咁<br />\n例：我都ん知樓主はいどう做まきゅ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將一啲唔知點寫嘅字用假名表達<br />\n<br />\n2. 搵返/ 作個正字出嚟<br />\n例：我都毋知樓主兮道做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f284a94da6556566517a60afe2b96b00cd3bdfce","tid":300869,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T22:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Jik jip seh ping yum ng lun ho?</blockquote><br />\nzek zip</blockquote><br />\n大陸喱先會用z開頭囉<br />\n<br />\n仲有zip 點撚樣發到個  接  音出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc26d5403a1189125c653b59168bfeea73580e2","tid":300869,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T22:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得漢字先係最適合廣東話 拼音個啲都係旁門左道<br />\n你個表啲新字母好似泰文咁 複雜又唔夠漢字清晰</blockquote><br />\n漢字真係又靚又好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有兩個方向可以做<br />\n<br />\n1. 假名化，好似樓主咁<br />\n例：我都ん知樓主はいどう做まきゅ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將一啲唔知點寫嘅字用假名表達<br />\n<br />\n2. 搵返/ 作個正字出嚟<br />\n例：我都毋知樓主兮道做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就真係唔知你係到做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解一定要正字先係正確？高級啲？<br />\n大眾用既就要夾硬改？<br />\n<br />\n一定要跟引經據典？將不合時宜既字套落已經成雛型既廣東話文法到？"}]}